-McZJdr65jDmAXtz0c0n.entry: I tripped I was on a bus so we were doing homework. The homework was black or white? When they music was turned up loud in the face was high the homework for it crawl on the signs and colors were glowing. I knew it was always a dream when I had to go to the bathroom and I turned into a home I ended up going to the bathroom and Jon‘s bathroom which definitely was not our bathroom andI was peeing while standing up in to agree. Jon walked in I thought that was pretty rude He laughed and said why I decided to use his bathroom. I was confused and asked him why he was in the bathroom in the first place I was going to the bathroom. I thought that was really odd in a flash and where I woke upit was 5:50 AM and I thought My alarm clock would go off soon. So I fell back asleep but it was 730. I went back to sleep again and then I woke up and it was 10 AM. I was worried about being late for class and then I realized that there would be no way I woke up at 5:50 AM and then all the sudden it was 10 AM I was really confused on that and thought this must be in the cityAnd then that’s when I woke up for real and realized that it was all a dream.
-McZJdr65jDmAXtz0c0n.name: 10 O’clock
-McZJdr65jDmAXtz0c0n.realization: I feel like the assignments and homework in my dream was pretty easy I had it all day and I try to help people with it but I also knew I was slacking off I ended up leaving the bus and doing other things. I think there was snow hunting in it but that might be because my son had referred to snails earlier that day in real life.

-McwTcFKMlwod12F7pke.entry:
I would say an in between dream types. Some parts were good, some were stressful and gave me anxiety. Carefree and fun, then stressful. Weirdly enough my current Gf, a few high school friends, my Mom, and my Dog were there lol. This took place a some weird Sports Arena/ Outdoor Amusement park. I was rolling my large Pc around on an office chair? lmao

We were walking around, having fun. Then went to the Southern Side, which had a paved walking road. On both sides of this road was land. There were dangerous animals like Lions, tigers, wolves, and others. Apparently this was a petting Zoo, though?!?! I was walking the path with my dog and this when the Anxiety started. He started leaving my side and I was worried bc I thought he was going to be eaten. After that, snow starting rolling in and everyone was gone. I was getting glimpse of the animals in and out of the snowy air. It was weird lol
-McwTcFKMlwod12F7pke.name: Wild Ride
-McwTcFKMlwod12F7pke.people: your current girlfriend, a few high school friends, my Mom, and my dog

-MeBA0gB2BdakVpS19kA.addDetails: There were twins, they may have been ghosts?
-MeBA0gB2BdakVpS19kA.entry: I dreamt I was isolated at a hotel in Colorado, I was hoping to cure my writer's block. My husband, Jon and our two sons were there. One of my sons becomes plagued with psychic premonitions. As my writing deteriorates my sons visions become more disturbing. I start to discover the hotel we are staying at has dark secrets and I begin to unravel into a homicidal maniac, hell-bent on terrorizing my family.
-MeBA0gB2BdakVpS19kA.name: The Shimmering
